Key Purpose <code>hyperparameter_tuner</code> Wraps any model above with grid, random, Optuna, or halving search <p>Example:</p> <pre><code>{
  "type": "random_forest_classifier",
  "node_id": "model_node",
  "params": {
    "n_estimators": 200,
    "max_depth": 10
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>Tuner example:</p> <pre><code>{
  "type": "hyperparameter_tuner",
  "base_model": {"type": "logistic_regression"},
  "strategy": "optuna",
  "search_space": {"C": [0.1, 1.0, 10.0]},
  "n_trials": 25,
  "metric": "accuracy"
}
</code></pre> <p>See "Modeling Nodes" in Reference for details.</p>
